<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Landing Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            background-color: #00bfff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #007acc;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Your Awesome Product</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our landing page</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam quis justo vel tellus efficitur tincidunt.
            Maecenas bibendum libero non cursus fringilla.</p>
        <a href="#cta" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
    </section>

    <section id="cta">
        <h2>Sign Up Now!</h2>
        <p>Join us and experience the amazing features of our product. Don't miss out!</p>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">Sign Up</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 Your Awesome Product. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
